{
  "info": {
    "name": "Order & Payment Management API - Complete Documentation",
    "description": "# Order & Payment Management API\n\n## Overview\nComplete API documentation for the Laravel-based Order and Payment Management system.\n\n## Features\n- JWT Authentication\n- Order Management (CRUD)\n- Payment Processing (Multiple Gateways)\n- Extensible Architecture\n\n## Base URL\n`http://localhost:8000/api`\n\n## Authentication\nAll protected endpoints require JWT token in Authorization header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {your_jwt_token}\n```\n\n## Available Payment Gateways\n- `credit_card` - Credit Card Processing\n- `paypal` - PayPal Integration\n- `stripe` - Stripe Payment Gateway\n\n## Status Codes\n- `200` - Success (GET, PUT, PATCH)\n- `201` - Created (POST)\n- `204` - No Content (DELETE)\n- `401` - Unauthorized\n- `403` - Forbidden\n- `404` - Not Found\n- `422` - Validation Error\n- `500` - Server Error",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12345678"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
