            "description": "Process credit card payment for an order.\n\n**Prerequisites:**\n- Order must be in 'confirmed' status\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `payment_method` (string, required): Must be 'credit_card'\n- `card_number` (string, required): Credit card number\n- `card_expiry` (string, required): MM/YY format\n- `card_cvv` (string, required): 3-digit CVV\n\n**Success Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Payment processed successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 1,\n    \"payment_method\": \"credit_card\",\n    \"status\": \"successful\",\n    \"amount\": \"2719.94\",\n    \"transaction_id\": \"credit_card_abc123_1706624000\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2025-01-30T10:05:00.000000Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Error Response (422):**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Payment processing failed\",\n  \"error\": \"Cannot process payment for order with status: pending. Order must be confirmed first.\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success - Payment Processed",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Payment processed successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 1,\n    \"payment_method\": \"credit_card\",\n    \"status\": \"successful\",\n    \"amount\": \"2719.94\",\n    \"transaction_id\": \"credit_card_abc123_1706624000\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2025-01-30T10:05:00.000000Z\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2025-01-30T10:05:00.000000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            },
